<a-modal
  title="分屏"
  :width="modalWidth"
  :visible="visible"
  :bodyStyle="bodyStyle"
  style="top: 0px;"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭">

  <split-pane :min-percent='20' :default-percent='50' split="vertical">
    <template slot="paneL">
      <split-panel-a></split-panel-a>
    </template>
    <template slot="paneR">
      <split-panel-b></split-panel-b>
    </template>
  </split-pane>

</a-modal>
